summary: So I just saw a clip from Sarah Jane Adventures with David Tennant, and Sarah says to The Doctor “No one’s ever going to forget...
body: So I just saw a clip from Sarah Jane Adventures with David Tennant, and Sarah says to The Doctor “No one’s ever going to forget you” but it takes place a year after Journey’s End so Donna is still fresh in his mind and I have too many feels.
